g/resource/Public_Protector\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parliament's ethics committee\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"a complaint\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response to a written question from DA MP Liam Jacobs, McKenzie said: \\\"Yes, I attended the 2024 Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1207, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Gallagher\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.863965226171671e-13, \"text\": \"Liam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Gallagher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Gallagher\"}, {\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998826752, \"rank\": 1.1749720864975053e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"a written question\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The total costs incurred by the department for my attendance at the Games amounted toR804 590.71\\\".\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The total costs\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"the department\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"my attendance\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His response also included atable(as below) breaking down the costs addressed to the Acting Director-GeneralCynthia Khumalo.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His response\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"atable(as\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"the costs\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"the Acting Director-GeneralCynthia Khumalo\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It showed the department spent R215 976.36 on his flights and R454 005.00 on his \\\"ground transport\\\".\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the department\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"his flights\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"his \\\"ground transport\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Accommodation totalled R113 271.00, subsistence and travel allowance was R20 745.72, while insurance was a comparatively low R592.63.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Accommodation\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"R113\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"insurance\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"a comparatively low R592.63\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gayton McKenzie appears to be struggling to remember whether or not he was in fact at the 2024 Paris Olympics - and which events he attended.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1748, \"end\": 1763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gayton McKenzie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The minister initially took to social platform X, denying that he attended the Olympics apart from the Opening Ceremony along the Seine River.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1994, \"end\": 2010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999554012001917, \"rank\": 2.3069949654873808e-05, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The minister\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1903}, {\"ngram\": \"social platform X\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"the Seine River\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in a subsequent post, he changed his tune somewhat, remembering he watched hockey, gymnastics and rugby sevens, as well as adding that he attended meetings, went to the athletes villa(ge) and opened the Ekhaya village.\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a subsequent post\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"his tune\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"hockey\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"meetings\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes villa(ge\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ekhaya village\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his letter to his Acting Director-General Cynthia Khumalo, McKenzie wrote that: \\\"My hotel costs also seem very steep, given that I asked not to be put in a five-star hotel, to save on costs.\\\"\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2309, \"end\": 2316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Lennon\", \"score\": 0.9999933927956588, \"rank\": 6.607248154331902e-06, \"text\": \"Cynthia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Lennon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Lennon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his letter\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"My hotel costs\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"a five-star hotel\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"costs\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said he stayed in the four-starHotel Lumenin Paris.\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2508, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998826752, \"rank\": 1.1749720864975053e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Late on Wednesday evening, McKenzie once again took to X to attempt to provide a more detailed breakdown of his costs - and time in Paris.\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2648, \"end\": 2653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998826752, \"rank\": 1.1749720864975053e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wednesday evening\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"a more detailed breakdown\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"his costs\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It now appears that the vast majority of the 'Ground Transport' figures was due to 'daily chauffer services'.\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vast majority\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'Ground Transport' figures\", \"from\": 2